list.abstract: winner，是YG Entertainment在2014年8月1日推出的韩国男子组合，由姜昇润、金秦禹、李昇勋、宋旻浩四名成员组成。 2014年8月12日，WINNER发行首张正规专辑《2014 S/S》。2015年9月6日至10月25日，WINNER在日本的东京、大阪等10个城市举行巡演。2016年2月1日，发行迷你专辑《EXIT:E》。2017年4月8日，WINNER出道后首次参加音乐节目《音乐中心》，正式回归乐坛。2018年1月10日，获得第32届金唱片奖音源部门本奖。4月4日，发行第二张正规专辑《EVERYD4Y》。2019年4月26日，出任2019曼谷韩流博览会形象大使。2022年7月10日，在首尔汝矣岛汉江公园举行“Holiday in city”演唱会。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, look. See? Even I'm a winner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦看，看到了吗? 我也是个赢家呢。

yingyinNormal.en: And our debate winner is Farkle Minkus!
yingyinNormal.zh: 本次辩论赛的胜者是法尔科·明克斯！

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, now you're talking like a winner!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看，你现在说话的口气才像个把妹高手!

yingyinNormal.en: George is the winner. Hooray. Well done, George.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治是冠军。好耶！做得好，乔治。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone's costume is very good. Hurray. Now you say who the winner is. Oh, yes. And the winner is me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个人的装扮都非常棒。好嘞 。现在你来公布谁胜出了。胜出的人是，我。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone's costume is very good. Hurray. Now you say who the winner is. Oh, yes. And the winner is me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个人的装扮都非常棒。好嘞 。现在你来公布谁胜出了。胜出的人是，我。

yingyinNormal.en: We have a winner. Who has this sports page? That's George's boat. George's the winner. I like boats, and I like paper boats the best. Me too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一名到了。体育版的纸船是谁的？那是乔治的纸船。乔治是第一名。我喜欢船，但我最喜欢的是纸船。我也是！

yingyinNormal.en: You want to endorse a winner, especially one you appointed to his position.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想支持一个赢家，尤其是你任命的人。

yingyinNormal.en: So Zaza is the winner. Hurray. You've got a medal. It's made of real plastic gold.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以最后是莎莎赢了。太棒了。你赢了一块奖牌。他可是真的用金色塑料做成的。

yingyinNormal.en: Hooray. Come on, Daddy, Mummy, come on, hurry. And my Mummy is the winner. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好耶，快点，爸爸，妈妈，快点。好耶。我妈妈是冠军。好耶。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I gotta tell you, I think you got a real winner with Priya. Yeah, me, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不得不说，我觉得你找上普丽娅真是太幸运了。我也这么想。

yingyinNormal.en: What shall we play now? Let's have a bicycle race. With a big, shiny cup for the winner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们现在该玩什么呢。我们来比赛骑自行车怎么样。赢了的人就可以得到一个亮闪闪的大奖杯。

yingyinNormal.en: What shall we play now? Let's have a bicycle race. With a big, shiny cup for the winner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们现在该玩什么呢？我们来比赛骑自行车怎么样。赢了的人就可以得到一个亮闪闪的大奖杯。

yingyinNormal.en: Richard Rabbit has jumped further than George. And the winner is Richard Rabbit. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小兔理查德跳得比乔治远。获胜的是小兔理查德。好嘞！

yingyinNormal.en: The friends have all finished together. Everyone is a winner. But we've only got one cup.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小朋友们一起到达了终点。每个人都是冠军。可是我们只有一个奖杯怎么办。

yingyinNormal.en: The friends have all finished together. Everyone is a winner. But we've only got one cup.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小朋友们一起到达了终点。每个人都是冠军。可是我们只有一个奖杯怎么办。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa, stop talking and run. Keep running, go on. And the winner is Emily Elephant. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇，不要讲话了，快跑。快跑，加油。获胜的是小象艾米丽。好嘞。

yingyinNormal.en: A magician never reveals his secrets. But surely a future Nobel Prize winner can figure it out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 魔术师是不会透露他的秘密的，但未来的诺奖得主肯定能搞明白的。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, the weirdest place would have to be the foot of the bed. Step back. We have a winner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，最奇怪的地方是床脚。真没意义。我们有优胜者了。

yingyinNormal.en: The winner and new leader of the seventh grade of John Quincy Adams middle school is... Hold on!
yingyinNormal.zh: 约翰·昆西·亚当斯中学七年级竞选胜者暨新领导人... 且慢！
